    <subfield code="y">00000 \it One-loop Feynman diagrams contributing at low energy to the effective magnetic interactions, in the SM (left) and beyond (right). In the latter case we have shown, for illustrative purposes, the case of SUSY models. The crosses denote a mass insertion.</subfield>
